pinctrl: sh-pfc: r8a77980: Deduplicate VIN1 pin definitions

Use union vin_data12 and VIN_DATA_PIN_GROUP() to reduce redundancies in
pin definitions for the VIN1 channel.

This reduces kernel size by 144 bytes.

